erent\nX-ray spectra, a decomposition into two different microstructured materials is\npossible. Similar to dual-energy imaging, the additional\nmicrostructure-specific information could be useful for clinical diagnosis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Jul 2020 16:23:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-29"}
