e of ideology in the formation of\nopinions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Jul 2020 16:39:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Feb 2021 20:19:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-03"}
