ation results validate that the proposed OAM reception scheme can\neliminate the effect of the misalignment error of a practical OAM channel and\napproaches the performance of an ideally aligned OAM channel.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Jul 2020 05:01:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 4 Jul 2020 05:43:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-07"}
