ion of the\n  perturbation modes in the present model is considerably\n  difficult. One has to modify the present model to provide a\n  consistent scheme of quantization of the perturbation modes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Jul 2020 06:23:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Dec 2020 09:45:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 2 Aug 2022 14:30:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-03"}
