erage transmission, ${\\cal T}_{\\rm ave}(E)$, for\nnanodevices which have nearly the desired quantum properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Jul 2020 12:18:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-03"}
